node.text: @wristaficionado has now available the most sought Richard Mille RM1103 rose gold flyblack 🔥 The 42mm rose gold case features a skeletonized dial with white numerals, offering analog time function, flyback chronograph, 60-minute countdown timer and oversized date display. It is equipped with a skeletonized automatic winding RMAC3 calibre, dual time, a power reserve of 55 hours, date display and flyback chronograph. The black rubber bracelet embodies the signature aesthetics of the brand.

The all new @Jacobandco Astronomia Everest Experience Made out in collaboration with the Swedish climber Johan Ernst Nilson 🧗‍♂️ 

Open the box and the Astronomia Everest appears to be imbedded in ice, and a speaker plays the sound of the Everest wind, recorded live on the mountain.

Inside the dome you can find water from both the North and South Poles and a piece of rock from Mount Everest that the Swedish climber personally collected.

Limited Edition to only 12 pieces
⌚️tag price: $885,000.00

NBA Hall of Famer Michael Jordan recently spotted wearing a full white custom Rolex Daytona Cosmograph designed and manufactured by Bamford Watch department ⚪️
Based on the Daytona model, Bamford Rolex Polar Watch take this classic design and cover them in a coat of white. 
The case and matching bracelet receive a Graphite Particle Coating to guarantee that their white hue lasts as long as the timepiece ticks. The dial is given a similar white makeover, with details like the markers, text, and hands in contrasting bursts of color to ensure legibility and add visual interest.
Limited Edition to just 10 pieces worldwide 
⌚️tag price: $55,000.00
•
📸 @vertigo1983

@jacobandco Caviar Tourbillon blue Camouflage is so spectacularly flawless and a beautiful combination between the finest gemsetting and haute horlogerie 💎
Every component and every side of the 18K white gold case has to be specifically prepared to accommodate the exceptionally accurate cut stones to ensure a perfect fit - not once or twice, but over 800 times.
A coming together of haute Jewellery and haute horlogerie know-how like no other.⠀⠀
Fully set with 424 baguette-cut blue sapphires in varying hues to achieve the camo effect, this Caviar Tourbillon combines absolutely intense aesthetics with the haute de gamme gemsetting and watchmaking know-hows. 
This timepiece embodies the art of invisible gem setting. 👌🏼
Limited Edition to just 18 pieces worldwide 
⌚️tag price: $730,000.00
